OL,5, A man whose son was injured in a crush 
OL,6, at a school gate has criticised its    
OL,7, handling of the incident.              
OL,9,FGordano School in Portishead, near     
OL,10,FBristol, says the gate was not open in 
OL,11,Ftime at the end of the school day on   
OL,12,FMonday so a "surge" led to injuries.   
OL,14,FGlyn said his son had two black eyes   
OL,15,Fand print marks on parts of his body   
OL,16,Ffrom other students' shoes.            
OL,18,FThe school says it is investigating    
OL,19,Fwhat happened and will update the      
OL,20,Fcommunity.                             
